OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781524080
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into school stabbing
OL,6,FCounter terrorism police is now
OL,7,Fleading an investigation into a school
OL,8,Fstabbing which saw two teenage pupils
OL,9,Fand a teacher injured.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to reports of the
OL,12,Fstabbing at the Co-Op Academy, in
OL,13,FBlackley, Manchester on 9 June.
OL,15,FTwo 14-year-olds - a girl and a boy -
OL,16,Fand a 27-year-old teacher were taken
OL,17,Fto hospital with injuries following
OL,18,Fthe incident, but have since been
OL,19,Fdischarged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
