PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781524080
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into school stabbing
OL,6,FA 14-year-old girl was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of section 18 assault and
OL,8,Fdetained under the Mental Health Act -
OL,9,Fbut following an assessment by health
OL,10,Fprofessionals she has been released
OL,11,Finto police custody.
OL,13,FIn a statement Greater Manchester
OL,14,FPolice (GMP) said: "As a result of
OL,15,Ffurther enquiries, Counter Terrorism
OL,16,FPolicing North West have now taken
OL,17,Fprimacy for the investigation with the
OL,18,Fsupport of Greater Manchester Police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781524080
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into school stabbing
OL,6,F"Searches relating to the
OL,7,Finvestigation remain ongoing and
OL,8,Fcounter terrorism detectives are
OL,9,Fkeeping an open mind to the motivation
OL,10,Fof the attack."
OL,12,FIt added: "At this time, it has not
OL,13,Fbeen declared as a terrorist incident."
OL,15,FThe three people who were injured have
OL,16,Fall been released from hospital and
OL,17,Fdid not suffer serious injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
