OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781524080
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into school stabbing
OL,6,FChief Superintendent David Meeney,
OL,7,FCommander for Manchester, said: "Our
OL,8,Flocal detectives have been
OL,9,Finvestigating this incident at pace
OL,10,Fever since we arrested a schoolgirl
OL,11,Fsuspect on Tuesday morning. She
OL,12,Fremains in custody in Manchester.
OL,14,F"This has included ensuring the
OL,15,Fsuspect is checked by health
OL,16,Fprofessionals to make an assessment
OL,17,Fwhile under the Mental Health Act, and
OL,18,Fto explore all available evidence to
OL,19,Funderstand why this incident took
OL,20,Fplace.
OL,26,@oD@aOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
