OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781524080
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into school stabbing
OL,6,F"Since our last update, further
OL,7,Finformation has come to light that we
OL,8,Fhave made Counter Terrorism Policing
OL,9,FNorth West aware of.
OL,11,F"I know this update will only continue
OL,12,Fto make our local community concerned
OL,13,Fby Tuesday's events.
OL,15,F"There is no information to indicate
OL,16,Fany further threat, and our local
OL,17,Fofficers continue to be in the area.
OL,18,FWe are here to listen and to act, so
OL,19,Fplease speak to our officers with any
OL,20,Fconcerns."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU|D@JO]
